import React from "react";
import { Modal } from "react-bootstrap";

import Button from "../button/Button";

const Form = () => {
	return (
		<Modal show={true} size="lg">
			<Modal.Header closeButton>
				<Modal.Title>Agrega un personaje</Modal.Title>
			</Modal.Header>
			<Modal.Body>
				<Form>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>Nombre</Form.Label>
						<Form.Control type="text" />
						<Form.Text className="text-muted">
							We'll never share your email with anyone else.
						</Form.Text>
					</Form.Group>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>Cumplea√±os</Form.Label>
						<Form.Control type="date" />
					</Form.Group>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>Color de Ojos</Form.Label>
						<Form.Control type="text" />
					</Form.Group>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>Color de Pelo</Form.Label>
						<Form.Control type="text" />
					</Form.Group>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>G√©nero</Form.Label>
						<Form.Check inline label="Mujer" name="genero" type="radio" />
						<Form.Check inline label="Hombre" name="genero" type="radio" />
					</Form.Group>
					<Form.Group controlId="">
						<Form.Label>Posici√≥m</Form.Label>
						<Form.Check
							inline
							label="Estudiante"
							name="estudiante"
							type="radio"
						/>
						<Form.Check inline label="Staff" name="estudiante" type="radio" />
					</Form.Group>
					<Button>Guardar</Button>
				</Form>
			</Modal.Body>
		</Modal>
	);
};

export default Form;
